name: Cosmic Consciousness
description: Humanity is spiritually evolving. You can see in everyone's focus on mental health and overcoming trauma, we are on a path to healing and renewal. And then what? As each person is able we wake them up to their ability to create the life they always wanted through the use of their imagination and the power of assumption. Humanity is preparing to dream the most beautiful dream we've ever created. I feel it every day and it excites me. We're swiftly getting ready to grow into the beings we were always meant to be and it's going to gorgeous. I love it.
